title: Start it off with a bang (Super Auto Pets)

media:group.media:title: Start it off with a bang (Super Auto Pets)
media:group.media:description:
Super Auto Pets on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1714040/Super_Auto_Pets/

This came from my stream on November 4th, 2022. Catch me live every weekday from 9AM-2PM here: http://twitch.tv/Northernlion

Super Auto Pets is a cute free autobattler (like Teamfight Tactics) that is really cute and has some strategic depth. Give it a try, you may be surprised by how much it mooves you!
